Package org.e2immu.support

Class Either<A,​B>

java.lang.Object
org.e2immu.support.Either<A,​B>
Type Parameters:
A - The type of the left object.
B - The type fo the right object.
public class Either<A,​B> extends Object
An class holding either an object of type A, or one of type B; it cannot hold both, nor can it hold neither.

Either is level 2 immutable, because its fields are explicitly final, and of implicit immutable type (unbound parameter type).

This is an example class! Please extend and modify for your needs.
